---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Home"
  description="Unlock your potential by understanding the power of your subconscious mind. Discover peace, clarity, and purpose."
>
  <section class="text-center py-20 lg:py-32">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-text-base leading-tight mb-4">
        Unstuck for Good. A Direct Path to Your Subconscious to Resolve Chronic Pain, Anxiety, and Limiting Patterns.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-text-muted max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
        For those who have tried everything, this powerful, eyes-open method helps you communicate directly with your inner mind to reclaim complete control of your health and life.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center items-center gap-4">
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-brand-primary text-white font-semibold py-3 px-8 rounded-full hover:bg-teal-700 transition-colors text-lg w-full sm:w-auto">
          Book a Free Consultation
        </a>
        <a href="/services" class="border border-brand-primary text-brand-primary font-semibold py-3 px-8 rounded-full hover:bg-brand-primary hover:text-white transition-colors text-lg w-full sm:w-auto">
          Learn About My Method
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-text-base mb-4">Your Journey to a Calmer Mind Starts Here</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted mb-4">
          [A paragraph introducing the philosophy of Hello Subconscious. Explain that many of our challenges—anxiety, self-doubt, and unwanted habits—stem from deep-seated subconscious patterns.]
        </p>
        <p class="text-text-muted">
          [Continue by explaining how your unique approach helps clients gently access and reframe these patterns, leading to lasting change and a more peaceful existence.]
        </p>
        <a href="/about" class="text-brand-primary font-semibold mt-6 inline-block hover:text-teal-700">
          Learn More About My Approach &rarr;
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="bg-slate-200 h-80 w-full rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
          <p class="text-text-muted">Calm & Minimalist Visual</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

